                                            Username
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding:0;color:#153643;text-align: center;color: #302D86;">
                                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight: 500;border: 1px solid #F5F5F5;padding: 10px; background-color: #F5F5F5;">
                                            @Model.Email
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>



                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 80px 0px 80px;">
